{"tid":1087373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共戰機飛越台灣海峽， 韓國瑜拒絕評論","createTime":"2019-04-01T10:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T14:07:58.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"77091f844c49d3f2faf54566a8b8003c4ddf84fb","tid":1087373,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:15:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=520554&amp;fbclid=IwAR1cPblmWr9UM-_rZKehg0IpYwKVADOUcJUKfaVqIou3EFmUV8Tm5J40zlk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D520554%26fbclid%3DIwAR1cPblmWr9UM-_rZKehg0IpYwKVADOUcJUKfaVqIou3EFmUV8Tm5J40zlk&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQixSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=634cdc98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D520554%26fbclid%3DIwAR1cPblmWr9UM-_rZKehg0IpYwKVADOUcJUKfaVqIou3EFmUV8Tm5J40zlk&h=b323c17e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=520554&amp;fbclid=IwAR1cPblmWr9UM-_rZKehg0IpYwKVADOUcJUKfaVqIou3EFmUV8Tm5J40zlk</a><br />\n<br />\n不敢惹中國？共機越線犯眾怒！韓國瑜：我滿腦在想芭樂銷售<br />\n2019/04/01 12:04:00<br />\n<br />\n政治中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n針對共軍2架殲11戰機，31日上午11時越過台灣海峽中線，並進入台灣西南面空域事件，總統蔡英文對此提出嚴重抗議，並提醒北京當局不要刻意挑釁、不要製造事端、不要試圖破壞台海的現狀。不過才剛訪問中國回來的高雄市長韓國瑜，1日在市議會備詢後受訪，竟然針對共機越線，給了答非所問的「神回應」，讓現場媒體相當錯愕。<br />\n<br />\n高雄市長韓國瑜1日前往市議會，進行施政報告與備詢，休息時間媒體訪問韓國瑜，針對「共軍越過海峽中線挑釁」的看法，沒想到韓國瑜先愣了一下，回答「其實我現在滿腦子，在想芭樂怎麼銷售耶，哈哈」，接著韓國瑜話鋒一轉，認為針對芭樂的銷售，農糧署的態度有問題。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜也強調，過去所有幫助農民的人，不管中央或地方，高雄市政府都樂觀其成也很感謝，韓國瑜直說「我從來沒有小鼻子小眼睛過」，過去前朝政府把通路打出來，接著韓國瑜也會把基礎加深加厚加大。"},{"pid":"a65073f33906e5de263ef62a841c5fd59e98d4c9","tid":1087373,"uid":38904,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:25:54.000Z","msg":"高雄: 只要付錢就可以給解放軍軍機上了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67339752f2c916c5010ed3533f23ef49c91cb4ba","tid":1087373,"uid":130695,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:30:51.000Z","msg":"佢全家都只係收錢做雞既<br />\n肯比錢叫隻狗屌佢都得啦"},{"pid":"33555014d782b4e6c3c48b13d3b07d847785ba8c","tid":1087373,"uid":4826,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:34:14.000Z","msg":"韓：戰機黎買水果返大陸"},{"pid":"fa57606875dcb80349204bc30ed4bd09373b99d4","tid":1087373,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T06:19:39.000Z","msg":"美國政府: 反對中共戰機飛越台灣海峽, 中共企圖片面改變現狀的做法有害<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ftvnews.com.tw/news/detail/2019402I04M1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftvnews.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F2019402I04M1&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQixSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=c7f4931e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ftvnews.com.tw/news/detail/2019402I04M1</a>"},{"pid":"de417e98e81f01337dab7dd0adf97abaeb64fdb0","tid":1087373,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T06:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d2bf35f47451f5029286145b111beb17d54ae7","tid":1087373,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T06:32:16.000Z","msg":"19才子點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3ac18da855186d9a25b31bc3b321f31f975817","tid":1087373,"uid":124277,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T06:33:30.000Z","msg":"係自已地方飛都要問人?"},{"pid":"1e8499b0f86ea06060d9807b5b9c5fe81ac28bec","tid":1087373,"uid":51057,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T06:37:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">芭樂出得去, 共軍進得來, 韓家發大財!</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8a77ffc0bbe52c98bd7af593817949cb0328498c","tid":1087373,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2d2bf35f47451f5029286145b111beb17d54ae7","tid":1087373,"uid":6